<refentry id="function.cpdf-continue-text">
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>cpdf_continue_text</refname>
  <refpurpose>Output text in next line</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
 <refsect1>
  <title>Description</title>
  <methodsynopsis>
   <type>bool</type><methodname>cpdf_continue_text</methodname>
   <methodparam><type>int</type><parameter>pdf_document</parameter></methodparam>
   <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>text</parameter></methodparam>
  </methodsynopsis>
  <para>
   The <function>cpdf_continue_text</function> function outputs the
   string in <parameter>text</parameter> in the next line. &return.success;
  </para>
  <para>
   See also <function>cpdf_show_xy</function>,
   <function>cpdf_text</function>,
   <function>cpdf_set_leading</function> and
   <function>cpdf_set_text_pos</function>.
  </para>
 </refsect1>
</refentry>

